The pfSense fwknop package provides GUI configuration and service integration
for fwknopd Single Packet Authorization.

It manages fwknopd settings, protected access stanzas, and package-generated
PF table allow rules so authenticated SPA clients can be added to temporary
allow tables without editing normal pfSense firewall rule arrays.

SPA can reduce exposed service surface area, but it is not a replacement for a
VPN or for strong service authentication.
